            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "id like to share my concerns as a student of this school. the main one being regarding the school washrooms. there is no nice way to put this but absolutely disgusting. there is no ventilation nor proper cleaning. there is an evident lack of privacy and is a very congested space. and this isnt one specific washroom but washrooms around the whole campus. and sanitary pads disposal is at a very pathetic condition. there used to be only one pad disposal machine in the ladies washroom which is also not functioning currently. this needs to be taken care immediately. to everybody whos contemplating on joining maharishi, kindly consider this issue.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
