            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My kid has joined maharishi Vidya mandir @ Thiruvarur branch... Highly dissatisfied... No proper coaching or no carrying... I donno how I'm gng to complete dis one year here... I made 5kids parents to join here. But now, I'm planning to get TC by next year. She studying grade 1 and she is 5years only. No proper carrying for kids. No aunty were sitting along with kids for lunch hours. Teachers texting me like, u have to teach ur kid to eat by herself.nan eh teach pandraduku nan yeduku school ku send pananum. After lock down, 1st time she gone to school.kids who were not eating themselves, aunty should feed them.but mam saying, no they have another work nu... Highly dissatisfied. Chetpet branch was always top in tamilnadu and by seeing that I was excited that thiruvarur they opened another branch. But in thiruvarur, MVM was not that much good in everything. Please takecare of kids and plz avoid opening during Saturdays atleast for primary children. Most of the schools were holiday today but my kid have school full day today and she studying grade 1 only.in thiruvarur MVM",
